**  (KOCD/KONM)
00-CANCEL
11-CHANGE
22-ADD
**  ER
E-01  UPDATE INSTRUCTION IS 0.1.2
E-02  RG CODE ISN'T INPUT
E-03  RG CODE ISN'T REGISTERED WITH M/F
E-04  ADD WAS APPOINTED, BUT M/F EXISTS
E-05  A CHANGE WAS APPOINTED, BUT M/F DOESN'T EXIST
E-06  A CHANGE WAS APPOINTED, BUT M/F IS CANCELLED ALREADY
E-07  A CANCELLATION WAS APPOINTED, BUT M/F DOESN'T EXIST
E-08  A CANCELLATION WAS APPOINTED, BUT M/F IS CANCELLED
E-09  SHIPMENT BIN NAME ISN'T INPUT
E-10  SETTING TIME(HOUR) ISN'T INPUT
E-11  SETTING TIME(HOUR) ISN'T RIGHT
E-12  SETTING TIME(MINUTES) ISN'T RIGHT
E-13  SETTING BIN ISN'T INPUT
